        <mxCell id="body" value="Your first Spring Boot REST API in 30 seconds:&amp;#xa;&amp;#xa;@RestController + @RequestMapping(&quot;/library&quot;)&amp;#xa;@GetMapping(&quot;/book&quot;) → List&lt;Book&gt; findAll()&amp;#xa;&amp;#xa;CRUD with H2 — no XML." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontColor=#e7e9ea;fontSize=13;spacingLeft=20;spacingTop=12;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
